590
00:52:57,754 --> 00:53:00,757
<i>Para pejabat dan polisi yang ada.</i>

591
00:53:00,840 --> 00:53:02,300
<i>Merekalah penjahatnya.</i>

592
00:53:02,926 --> 00:53:04,302
<i>Para warga negara sekalian.</i>

593
00:53:04,844 --> 00:53:05,970
<i>Buka mata kalian.</i>

594
00:53:07,764 --> 00:53:09,599
<i>Membuat senjata manusia?</i>

595
00:53:09,682 --> 00:53:11,434
<i>Itu hanya permainan mereka.</i>

596
00:53:11,517 --> 00:53:13,019
